{"tid":2373279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"未成年男女被控阻街 警員指男被告推木卡板協助堵路","createTime":"2021-01-20T10:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T12:22:17.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aef0473f6d3ad79aa29270aef1d4253a17e70c86","tid":2373279,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"示威者前年底在旺角洗衣街及山東街交界一帶堵路，警方其後驅散並拘捕多人，事後三名年輕男女被控堵路，一人早前認罪，獲判160小時社會服務令，案中同為17歲的男女則否認控罪，案件今日在西九龍裁判法院開審。警員作供時承認，<span class=\"red\">他拘捕的男被告沒有以木卡板堵路</span>，但謂：「係呀，佢冇掟呀，佢推出嚟，畀人掟出馬路之嘛。<br />\n<br />\n看過片段後，陳稱自己乘坐第一架衝鋒車抵達現場，但片中看不到男被告的身影，片段亦看不到他在山東街制服被告的過程。<br />\n<br />\n警員17101陳敏堂作供稱第一眼見到身處行人路上的男被告至他下車追截時，<span class=\"red\">視線沒有離開過男被告</span>。惟至盤問時被問及下車後是否需要轉身，陳才<span class=\"red\">改口稱曾經有一剎那男被告離開過他的視線</span>，其後又承認當時該地有人違例泊車，「係望向被告的方向沒有違例泊車情況」。<br />\n<br />\n陳憶述稱：「呢班人入面有人『睇水』， 有人喺度指揮，搬啲卡板垃圾出馬路。我就見到被告喺行人路幫手推啲木卡板，令啲示威者可以將啲木卡板掟出馬路。」"},{"pid":"5425ec0156fd587fa7d368a8533205235f329696","tid":2373279,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/DBOFSQDJD5HSTG5D7RZ22N5XIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FDBOFSQDJD5HSTG5D7RZ22N5XIU%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia4lS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=c733dccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FDBOFSQDJD5HSTG5D7RZ22N5XIU%2F&h=bc86b838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/DBOFSQDJD5HSTG5D7RZ22N5XIU/</a>"},{"pid":"6d5767a02bce4757513c49f83babd56c949c40f6","tid":2373279,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618eb18c03591c990171587a2c647dd3178d95cc","tid":2373279,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">警員17101陳敏堂</span>作供稱當下只是在車上「望左一眼」，故除了看到在搬運木卡板的曾身上衣著，沒有留意到其餘示威者的衣著或其他行為。<br />\n<br />\n陳堅稱，憑其背囊、衣著及跑步姿勢認出曾，指「佢跑步姿勢同一般人唔同，佢好似係度跳下跳下」，因此肯定曾在案發現場搬動木卡板。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/12-9-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8E%9F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A6%96%E7%B7%9A%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E7%9B%A4%E5%95%8F%E4%B8%8B%E6%94%B9%E7%A8%B1-%E4%B8%80%E5%89%8E%E9%82%A3%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%81%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F12-9-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2595%258F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2589%258E%25E9%2582%25A3%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2581%258E%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia4lS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=520f51a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F12-9-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2595%258F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2589%258E%25E9%2582%25A3%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2581%258E%2F&h=350de774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/12-9-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8E%9F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A6%96%E7%B7%9A%E7%84%A1